author: rwesten
msg: STANBOL-630: This adds a check to the EnhancementStructureHelper unit test utility that validates fise:confidence values are within [0..1]. It removes similar custom checks from UnitTests and configures fise:confidence as an required property for most of the other engines.
In addition it includes the following change to the OpenCalais engine:
* OpenCalais: enabled the calculate confidence feature to tell Calais that we want to receive confidences. Confidences are now added to the Enhancements created by this Engine
